trans-unit.source: Called by the <xref uid="langword_csharp_Dispose()" name="Dispose()" href=""></xref> and <xref uid="langword_csharp_Finalize()" name="Finalize()" href=""></xref> methods to release the managed and unmanaged resources used by the current instance of the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.FilteredCatalog"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: 由呼叫<xref uid="langword_csharp_Dispose()" name="Dispose()" href=""></xref>和<xref uid="langword_csharp_Finalize()" name="Finalize()" href=""></xref>釋放 managed 和 unmanaged 資源的目前執行個體所使用的方法<xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.FilteredCatalog"></xref>類別。

trans-unit.source: This method is called only by the public `Dispose()` and `Finalize()` methods; do not call this method directly.When you implement the dispose pattern, the Boolean parameter of the `Dispose(Boolean)` method should be used as follows: - The `Dispose()` method of the current object should call `Dispose(Boolean)` with the Boolean parameter set to `true` to release both managed and unmanaged resources.
trans-unit.target: 會呼叫這個方法只由公用`Dispose()`和`Finalize()`方法。 請勿直接呼叫這個方法。當您實作 dispose 模式的布林參數`Dispose(Boolean)`方法應使用，如下所示:-`Dispose()`目前物件的方法應該呼叫`Dispose(Boolean)`布林參數設定為與`true`表示釋放 managed 和 unmanaged 資源。

trans-unit.source: - The `Finalize()` method of the current object should call `Dispose(Boolean)` with the Boolean parameter set to `false` to release only unmanaged resources.
trans-unit.target: -`Finalize()`目前物件的方法應該呼叫`Dispose(Boolean)`布林參數設定為與`false`表示只釋放 unmanaged 的資源。

trans-unit.source: For more information, see .
trans-unit.target: 如需詳細資訊，請參閱。

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> to release managed and unmanaged resources; <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref> to release only unmanaged resources.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>表示釋放 managed 和 unmanaged 資源，<xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>表示只釋放 unmanaged 的資源。
